{"id": "tod1665702665614", "title": "setformfocus", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "setformfocus"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tod1665702665614.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">setformfocus</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: set \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: set \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eww1719683180873.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: setocc \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: setocc \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/tod1665702665614.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/tod1665702665614.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/tod1665702665614.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532449\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532449\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tod1665702665614.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tod1665702665614.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tod1665702665614.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tod1665702665614\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"tod1665702665614__setformfocus_239521\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the focus to the specified component instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tod1665702665614__topic_d77222e1_d77223e1_d77224e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tod1665702665614__p_d77225e1_d77226e1_d77227e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setformfocus</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"tod1665702665614__section_w2204ab1b7b5_w2205ab1b7_w2206ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tod1665702665614__p_d77228e1_d77229e1_d77230e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">setformfocus \"tab1\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tod1665702665614__topic_d50767e1_d50768e1_d50769e1_d50770e1_d50771e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d463689e77\">Parameters </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7406e1_d7407e1_d7408e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7406e1_d7407e1_d7408e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7406e1_d7407e1_d7408e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7406e1_d7407e1_d7408e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7406e1_d7407e1_d7408e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7406e1_d7407e1_d7408e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7406e1_d7407e1_d7408e1__entry__3\">\n Name of a Form instance in the component pool.\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tod1665702665614__li_d32978e1_d32979e1_d32980e1\">If omitted, focus is set to the current form instance<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tod1665702665614__li_d32981e1_d32982e1_d32983e1\">If longer than 16 characters, the form name is truncated to that length. Trailing blanks are removed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tod1665702665614__li_d32984e1_d32985e1_d32986e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> does not currently have focus, Uniface activates the loseFocus trigger of the form instance that loses focus and getFocus trigger of the form instance that receives focus.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tod1665702665614__topic_d50772e1_d50773e1_d50774e1_d50775e1_d50776e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d463689e149\">Return Values </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__2\">\n Focus change requested from component manager.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__2\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> is not in the\n                        component pool or is not correct (field or variable not found, or the string\n                        is not a valid instance name). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7409e1_d7410e1_d7411e1__entry__2\">\n A modal form has focus; <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setformfocus</span> cannot be used to change the focus.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Commonly Returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setformfocus</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Error constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code>  through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during network I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-57</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The named instance cannot be found in the component pool.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-405</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UMISERR_SETFORMFOCUS&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tod1665702665614__table_d7412e1_d7413e1_d7414e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Modal form has focus. In this\n                        case, <code class=\"ph codeph\">setformfocus</code>  cannot be used to change the focus. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tod1665702665614__topic_d50777e1_d50778e1_d50779e1_d50780e1_d50781e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d463689e334\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tod1665702665614__d6006e20\">Allowed in Form, Report, and Service components, but not in self-contained components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tod1665702665614__topic_d50782e1_d50783e1_d50784e1_d50785e1_d50786e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d463689e343\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tod1665702665614__p_d77246e1_d77247e1_d77248e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setformfocus</span> statement sends an\n            asynchronous request to the component manager to set the form focus to the requested\n            form instance. For example, it can be used to change form focus in a master-detail\n            construction. (For an example, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wtd1665702577667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wtd1665702577667.html\" title=\"Send a message from one component instance to another.\">postmessage</a>.)</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tod1665702665614__p_d77249e1_d77250e1_d77251e1\">To set focus to a form that represents a page of a tab widget, assign the instance name of the desired form to the tab widget field. However, you can also use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setformfocus</span> statement with the instance name of a contained form to make that page active.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"tod1665702665614__note_w2207ab1b7c13b7_w2208ab1b7c13_w2209ab1b7_w2210ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> Do not use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setformfocus</span> in the getFocus or\n            loseFocus triggers, or in processing that is initiated in these triggers. Doing so can\n            cause your application or the operating system to stop responding.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jnk1665702665688.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$formfocus</a><p>Return the name of the Form instance that has focus.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532449\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532449\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "setformfocus Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the focus to the specified component instance. setformfocus { InstanceName } Example: setformfocus \"tab1\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description InstanceName String Name of a Form instance in the component pool. If omitted, focus is set to the current form instance InstanceName . If longer than 16 characters, the form name is truncated to that length. Trailing blanks are removed. If InstanceName does not currently have focus, Uniface activates the loseFocus trigger of the form instance that loses focus and getFocus trigger of the form instance that receives focus. Return Values Table 2. Values Returned in $status Value Meaning 0 Focus change requested from component manager. <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. -1 InstanceName is not in the component pool or is not correct (field or variable not found, or the string is not a valid instance name). -2 A modal form has focus; setformfocus cannot be used to change the focus. Table 3. Values Commonly Returned by $procerror following setformfocus Value Error constant Meaning -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. -57 <UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE> The named instance cannot be found in the component pool. -405 <UMISERR_SETFORMFOCUS> Modal form has focus. In this case, setformfocus cannot be used to change the focus. Use Allowed in Form, Report, and Service components, but not in self-contained components. Description The setformfocus statement sends an asynchronous request to the component manager to set the form focus to the requested form instance. For example, it can be used to change form focus in a master-detail construction. (For an example, see postmessage .) To set focus to a form that represents a page of a tab widget, assign the instance name of the desired form to the tab widget field. However, you can also use the setformfocus statement with the instance name of a contained form to make that page active. CAUTION: Do not use setformfocus in the getFocus or loseFocus triggers, or in processing that is initiated in these triggers. Doing so can cause your application or the operating system to stop responding. Related Links $formfocus Return the name of the Form instance that has focus. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}